{"tid":734890,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"識搵一定搵讀土木工程既做男朋友","createTime":"2018-07-09T04:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T09:36:29.000Z","uid":57526,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ba87224c250df6567fb5de58b69042ccfe19ddb7","tid":734890,"uid":57526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"有一日,有個女仔朋友問我點揀男朋友好。 <br />\n<br />\n我一口就答佢: &ldquo;識搵一定搵讀土木工程的做男朋友&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n好多人誤會讀工程一定係毒拎,唔係毒拎就係大男人,粗粗魯魯,不懂溫柔。 <br />\n<br />\n其實全部都係誤解。 <br />\n<br />\n你以為佢地唔細心,我同你,講做工程的男仔可以細心到30層樓每條電線的位置都記得。 <br />\n<br />\n所以呢,女朋友就算問到佢 &ldquo;我今日有咩唔同左&rdquo;都可以輕鬆應付。 <br />\n<br />\n唔好話咩生日,拍拖紀念日,佢地連你m到都計得到。 <br />\n<br />\n有人話吃得苦中苦方為人上人, 讀工程男仔大概是這樣吧。 <br />\n<br />\n土木工程的男仔每日8點鐘就要到地盤工作, 對住一條二條鐵,一舊二舊石屎的時候, 你係邊? <br />\n<br />\n你仲訓緊覺呀! <br />\n<br />\n當你仲同人講緊 &ldquo;識條鐵咩你?&rdquo;的時候,佢地真係睇緊鐵圖啦! <br />\n<br />\n夏天的時候 30幾度行地盤, 冬天的時候落住冰雹睇石屎。 <br />\n<br />\n你話 ,一個中環老西友係佢地面前仲算唔算係男人。 <br />\n<br />\n仲有, 土木工程的男仔有經濟能力但唔會亂洗錢。Fresh grad 已經有20k唔再講,考埋牌50k話都無咁易。 <br />\n<br />\n由於佢地日日番工都對入住班男同事的關係, 放假都只仍會想陪女朋友。 <br />\n<br />\n咁的男人可以係邊搵? 佢地就算洗錢都只會洗係你身上。 <br />\n<br />\n比起日日浦LKF的西裝友, 撰邊個? 唔洗我講啦。 <br />\n<br />\n所以話,作為一個男人讀工程真係已經無得輸,仲要讀土木工程真係男人中的中男人 <br />\n<br />\n最後個女仔過左兩個月就同左個CIVIL仔一齊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3e72a42318a119567b7f216d51c4babd264a27","tid":734890,"uid":135445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"成地都係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262c234042d758ab09010e5c94ed1d1e50c9d864","tid":734890,"uid":124020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:58:20.000Z","msg":"舊文重溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa229aa56bc9e2be317436b42c07eb0a213ea8c6","tid":734890,"uid":11698,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:28:09.000Z","msg":"讀完工程一年就有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedb97af4b99c8a612102804844bf5dfb8200f38","tid":734890,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa229aa56bc9e2be317436b42c07eb0a213ea8c6","tid":734890,"uid":11698,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:28:09.000Z","msg":"讀完工程一年就有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"唔係讀civil冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e32ddf6307cdbea57cc38410b4b39138a8de79","tid":734890,"uid":46862,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fa229aa56bc9e2be317436b42c07eb0a213ea8c6","tid":734890,"uid":11698,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:28:09.000Z","msg":"讀完工程一年就有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"讀緊淨係得男朋友<br />\n讀完先有女朋友"},{"pid":"a778739764fb36bf6346c515d5098942196c49fc","tid":734890,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T09:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 作者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}